- Durable source: `kronos-preview.html`.
- Extraction date: 2026-06-28.
- License or redistribution note: user-provided local preview; abstract design
  semantics only.
- Extracted signals: cold metallic radial background, sticky dark nav, square
  monogram mark, frosted warm-champagne glass cards, cold blue accent, simple
  solution tabs, CAD-style viewport, three-card feature grid, metric dashboard,
  clean timeline, resource archive cards, corporate modal forms, bottom-right
  toast, and structured footer.
- Explicitly excluded: source asset references, font references,
  implementation snippets, concrete brand copy, concrete person names, concrete
  file names, phone/email actions, and any operable targets.

